Strategy Overview: Silver Early Pulse v11.0
Core Philosophy: This strategy is a momentum-based approach specifically optimized for the Silver (XAG/USD) market. Unlike lagging indicators, the "Early Pulse" system focuses on pre-emptive entries, identifying the initial "heartbeat" of a price surge before the main trend fully develops.

Key Characteristics
Asset: Silver (XAG/USD).

Timeframe: Optimized for Intraday (M5–M30) to capture volatility.

Entry Logic: Uses a proprietary blend of Volume Spread Analysis (VSA) and Relative Strength to detect institutional accumulation/distribution.

The "Pulse" Factor: It triggers entries when momentum deviates from the 20-period baseline, anticipating a breakout rather than waiting for a candle close above resistance.
